.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian, french, indonesian, argentine, italian, thai
7 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, frog, horse, guinea-pig, dog, hedgehog
 1. the argentine is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the thai##1
 4. the french is on the left of the italian##1
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 6. the indonesian is the owner of the horse##1
 7. the malaysian is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the hedgehog and the indonesian##2
 9. the malaysian is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
10. the egyptian is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | thai | argentine | malaysian | egyptian   | indonesian | french | italian |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | dog     | ferret     | frog | horse   | mouse   | hedgehog    |

