.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, mirinda, cola, 7up
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, brazilian, indonesian, argentine, colombian, turkish, american
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the indonesian##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the colombian##1
 3. the turkish is on the right of the argentine##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the colombian##1
 5. the dutch is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the argentine is between the person drinking almond-milk and the turkish##2
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is in the middle##1
 8. the argentine is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person drinking milk is the brazilian##1
10. the dutch is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | mirinda  | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk  | 7up      | cola       | milk |
| Nationality   | colombian | argentine | turkish | american | dutch | indonesian | brazilian  |

