.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, techno, funk, reggae, electronic, gospel, trance
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, airplane, snowmobile, scooter, jet-ski, bus, boat
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the fan of techno##1
3. the person driving the car is between the fan of trance and the fan of r&b##2
4. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
8. the person driving the airplane is the fan of reggae##1
9. the fan of electronic is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | electronic | r&b | funk | trance      | techno      | gospel |
| Transport     | airplane | bus | boat       | car | snowmobile | jet-ski | scooter |

