.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  architect, software-developer, librarian, teacher, security-guard, police-officer, chef
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, handball, ice-hockey, weightlifting, rugby, surfing
1. the librarian is on the left of the chef##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the security-guard##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the police-officer is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the architect##2
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
8. the police-officer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | security-guard | architect | teacher | police-officer | software-developer | librarian     | chef |
| Sport   | handball   | ice-hockey    | surfing    | weightlifting      | water-polo  | volleyball | rugby |

