.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, almond-milk, water, mirinda, tea, soy-milk
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: sailing, tennis, ice-hockey, biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, handball
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's sport is handball##2
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person drinking mirinda##2
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | sprite | 7up    | water | almond-milk   | tea | soy-milk    | mirinda |
| Sport      | biathlon | sailing | handball    | tennis | lacrosse    | ice-hockey | soccer  |

