.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, milk, iced-tea, soy-milk, coffee, 7up
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, coach, nurse, musician, analyst, doctor, journalist
 1. the analyst is on the left of the musician##1
 2. the electrician is on the left of the nurse##1
 3. the doctor is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the analyst is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking 7up##2
 7. the coach is on the right of the doctor##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking sprite##2
11. the analyst is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | milk  | soy-milk   | sprite         | tea     | 7up              | coffee    | iced-tea     |
| Job        | doctor | coach | analyst | musician | journalist | electrician | nurse |

