.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, family, drama, documentary, martial-arts, zombie, time-travel
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, train, airplane, car, subway, boat
1. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person driving the boat and the person driving the car##2
4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person driving the scooter is in the middle##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
7. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the car##1
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
9. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | documentary     | zombie | martial-arts | drama | time-travel  | scientific |
| Transport     | train | airplane | car   | scooter     | boat    | snowmobile | subway   |

