.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, water, soy-milk, lemonade, juice, iced-tea
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, chess, rock-climbing, collecting, puzzles, dancing, writing
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is chess##2
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | sprite       | iced-tea         | lemonade         | soy-milk   | water        | juice |
| Hobby      | writing | rock-climbing | woodworking | puzzles | chess | dancing | collecting  |

