3. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku       | fishing    | gardening | skydiving | card-games     | drawing       |
