.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: mystery, romance, comedy, disaster, superhero, sports, martial-arts
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: techno, rock, electronic, funk, blues, indie, country
 1. the person watching mystery movies is the fan of country##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the fan of techno##2
 4. the person watching sports movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
 5. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 6. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is the fan of blues##1
 9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
10. the fan of funk is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | mystery | romance  | superhero   | sports | martial-arts | comedy |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | country       | techno | electronic | indie  | rock   | blues   |

