 3. the person drinking milk is between the fan of d&b and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 4. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 5. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
