 5. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 6. the person eating garlic is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating peas##1
 8. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 9. the person drinking cucumberade is between the person drinking coffee and the person eating garlic##2
