 4. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person eating onion##2
 5. the person eating plum is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person eating radish is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person eating pumpkin is the person eating pumpkin##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
